      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\u2728 Pristine Mint Condition \u2014 A Rare Gem That's Ready to Wow! \u2728 This vehicle is as close to perfect as it gets on the used market \u2014 a true mint-condition beauty that has been exceptionally well cared for! The exterior is flawless, with paint that gleams and bodywork free of any notable blemishes or imperfections. Inside, the cabin feels fresh and immaculate \u2014 every surface, seat, and detail is in outstanding shape. Mechanically, this car runs like a dream, performing exactly as it should with no issues to report. If you've been searching for a used car that feels brand new, your search ends here. Don't miss your chance to own something truly special! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
